Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:04.40,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Night suddenly appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:09.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Real, but not real... just like a dark parallel world in a different space and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:13.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Knights attacked the boy and the girl, who had fallen down there, and called them “Fragments”.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.99,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of breeze has swept them into this sinister place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:19.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,By the end of this nightmare, will there be an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.25,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, he's from our school, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.33,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he get into a fight? Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:38.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I expected, time stood still in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:47.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it nice for you guys to be so carefree...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:03:01.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, welcome to the “Modern Societies Study Club” hosted by me, Yukiko Hirohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:07.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Modern Societies Study is the investigation and research of various phenomena in our modern society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:11.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it's a modern version of archeological research.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.84,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, finally the “Modern Societies Study Club” has new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls and one boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nee-san died seven years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I saw in the Red Night must have been an illusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.78,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, back then...{\i0}{\fad(0,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to fret over something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we are all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.76,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to meet so many allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan, you're amazing, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:07.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You've survived the Red Night all by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:07.93,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you have some kind of special power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.14,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm merely a normal girl, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.48,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,However, when I'm angry, I'm pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.28,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always cheerful, Yukiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:26.20,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only strong point that I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.20,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,where and with whom did you fight to get injured like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attendance is dropping pretty fast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.92,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been skipping classes lately, don't you want to graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop preaching, you're no more than an old hag who is still single.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:53.48,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa, I'm really glad that you'd never think of laying your hands on women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.65,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there, Takahisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.78,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Fragments...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.91,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Black Knights referred to us as "Fragments"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since you Fragments are about to disappear, I have no obligation to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.79,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean by “Fragments”?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, how many “Fragments” are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.42,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I know one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:26.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Red Night appeared the first time, someone called “The Ally of Justice” helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-kun, so you know her as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.77,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Things regarding that world and this ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.24,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.70,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's settled then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.25,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The task for today is to search for that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.54,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have already decided, let us not waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.46,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.71,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.13,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you hiding...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:08.22,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.43,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.47,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.31,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What was so urgent that...? You're so terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.81,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that “Ally of Justice"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.73,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.28,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the search has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.78,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people who can see the black moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.09,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Satsuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.71,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that you don't have any ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:55.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impressive that you've survived so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry. It was a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.14,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some fries?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.73,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.48,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.40,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.95,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.62,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has any detailed knowledge about the Red Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.79,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, see you guys later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.88,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Takahisa Tajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.17,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to join the Modern Societies Study Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak dogs join packs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.30,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in team work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he just call us dogs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.85,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the Red Night comes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.97,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll think of something by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.98,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an bad-mannered person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.53,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No, though he may look like that, he's actually pretty kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Very kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.20,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not horrible at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.29,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, people may really envy you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:28.48,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-senpai, you won’t be able to succeed if you swing it around aimlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.49,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Your impatience will confuse you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you are fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.46,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can protect Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.43,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it sounds sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:03.98,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words alone are not enough to achieve what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.73,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings are not transforming into power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:11.44,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the sword that you are holding carry your resolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.94,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Resolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your resolution that will enlighten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:20.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,However, your thoughts have not reached the stage of enlightenment yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.79,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the heart that requires training first, and not the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.54,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform your thoughts into power, and don't think about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.84,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.63,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Transform thoughts into power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.64,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.60,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in order to protect Yuka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:54.61,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.71,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:13.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... No... I wonder what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it were a real battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:21.18,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't have been able to protecting Yuka-san, you would've been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.39,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid you'd say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.39,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it was not intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.31,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.23,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:40.07,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to test Kakeru's resolution, I intended to attack her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:44.91,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His actions just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.64,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm embarrassingly weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I will definitely protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.98,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:19.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no power either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.87,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're by my side, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:34.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,“I want to protect Yuka”. I want to transform that thought into power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.96,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:40.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Ciao! Buongiorno, Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.89,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Piacere. Come sta, Shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.47,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Quanto costa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.60,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't speak such weird Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:54.90,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,To be in passionate, bilingual relationships with beautiful girls, I need to practice very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.82,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.07,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn until you turn to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.57,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, capito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:02.86,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiori-chan, isn't it “ladies first” in Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:10.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please walk straight down this road, turn right and die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Si. I will gladly do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Go straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.46,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.09,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.55,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrivederci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:22.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:27.60,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:33.94,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets any dumber, I don't know what to call him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.70,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.87,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:49.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka left a bit early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, about yesterday's training...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.41,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.39,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, welcome, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:15.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're in the middle of one of the club's activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.52,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:22.32,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Yuka-san have such big breasts, despite her small body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:25.99,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Yukiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.28,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,They are neither sagging, nor are they erect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.79,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Without any push-up bra, this is a modern miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:37.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she do that on sacred school ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukiko-chan, stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.71,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.73,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai is engaged in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:40.31,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai is a mental ignition type, a Pyrokineticist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.28,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,A Black Knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:58.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Fragments, you won't be so lucky today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly who are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:04.38,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say to the sinners who will eventually turn into dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,“Nothing to say”, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.47,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-kun, please take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.35,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanagiri Nagamitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.12,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy.... is using martial arts?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.45,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.66,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai is being pushed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It has begun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:51.17,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Avaritia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.14,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Fragments defeated Gula.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.89,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, Ira and Invidia are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.69,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, Superbia, am there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.49,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.08,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.62,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,But Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.84,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-senpai is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.67,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:34.80,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Just desiring power will not make you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.72,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in trouble unless you bring forth your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is somewhat like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.06,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yukiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,This speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.65,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an overwhelming fighting ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.74,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.04,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:04.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.50,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like she's a different person completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.91,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.91,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H894709&\c&HFFF7F0&}Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.03,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.74,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Invidia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:11.17,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that Ira could handle all the Fragments alone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.21,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You should all just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.26,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ally of Justice has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:36.61,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... do this to my face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.61,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.29,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Night is about to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.00,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.25,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we'll finish the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.44,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka... Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:23.36,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! Those wounds were too deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.01,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mess, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.64,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.30,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:50.72,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when I take my glasses off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.56,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,A split personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:59.40,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn that inhuman fighting ability and that killer instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.90,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.32,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to talk about it though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:07.16,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, are you hurt, Yukiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.74,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:13.62,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have the ability to regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.29,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.13,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.34,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's creepy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.77,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.73,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:40.11,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, everyone... about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:59.75,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in a country called Doresvenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.55,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a land full of chaos and killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.59,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.77,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,In all, four people have accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:19.10,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, and....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.37,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nah, it's not creepy at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.33,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, people probably envy you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.46,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you get hurt, you'll go right back to being okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.75,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1} Back to the beautiful girl you are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:50.51,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:52.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:56.22,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka-san, Kakeru-senpai, Misuzu-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:58.85,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:05.02,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahisa-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:09.24,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you at the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.59,0:24:47.55,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.55,0:24:51.27,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,For My Friends and For Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.27,0:24:55.05,11eyes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,777)}At the end of the nightmare, will there be an answer?
